<plot>Charlie, the 10-year-old "littlest expert", shows some newsreel shots of the horse-and-buggy days and comments on the customs, habits, life and times. And then concludes it is better for him to be a boy in modern times as he wouldn't have been able to collect bubble-gum cards in those days.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?423315</url></doc>
